Further from the centre, partly in the shadow, are the sports not generally recognized: air pistol shooting, archery, badminton, taekwondo.
We'll always have the breast-swimming and may it last.
But if I may humbly make arguments for my particular favourite, then let me draw your attention to the discreet charm of the trampoline.
